-Left flipper is so weak it can't send a ball more than halfway up the table! 

-Ball will get stuck in the Final Draw scoop until the machine runs a ball search and still won't count the shot. 

-Striker target will register hits by ANY movement. Hitting the flippers or touching the machine in any way. 

-The last 2 points combined allows for infinite points just by spamming the flippers with a ball stuck in Final Draw. 

I was playing on a very humid day so maybe that had a bit to do with it but really this machine needs to be taken out back and shot. Don't waste your time.
